edicinein these groupsfamous journalists and nonfiction authorsfamous people born on october famous librasfamous people in journalism  nonfictionshow all groupsfamous people in science and medicinefamous people who started businessesfamous people born in famous indiansfamous medical professionalsfamous people born in indiafamous people named deepakfamous people named choprafamous doctorsfamous people born in new delhiquotes“you must find the place inside yourself where nothing is impossible”deepak choprasynopsisthe author of numerous books on alternative medicine deepak chopra was born in new delhi india in  after attending the all india institute of medical sciences he eventually ended up in boston where he began his career as a doctor after becoming disenchanted with western medicine however chopra turned to alternative medicine in  chopra already a prolific book author founded the chopra center for well being in carlsbad californiaearly life and careerdeepak chopra was born on october   in new delhi india the son of an eminent cardiologist krishnan chopra deepak at first decided against following his fathers career path wanting instead to pursue a career as a journalist eventually however he became enthralled with the subject of medicine and enrolled at the all india institute of medical sciences in his native city chopra envisioned a career in western medicine and in  moved to the united states leaving his home country with just  in his pocket and the promise of a residency at a hospital in new jersey following the residency chopra landed in boston where he quickly rose to chief of medicine at new england memorial hospital despite his rising career chopra became disenchanted with western medicine and its reliance on prescription drugs the work began to wear on the promising doctor who would later claim that he smoked up to a pack of cigarettes a day and drank consistently very unhappy people physicians he has said the relatives of patients with whom they deal are demanding litigious intimidating thats the environment of medicine most of my fellow colleagues were very stressed a lot of them were addicts i used to experience the most extraordinary frustration and tightness my great fear was getting into trouble malpractice suits are a big deal in the united states its during this time that chopra read a book on transcendental medicine that changed his life and eventually his career path as his interest in alternative medicine deepened so did his view on the limits of western medicine after a meeting with transcendental mediation guru maharishi mahesh yogi chopra quit his job at new england memorial hospital and started the maharishi ayurveda products international a company that specialized in alternative products like herbal teas and oils cofounded with the maharishi the company successfully launched chopra into the world of alternative medicine chopra helped oversee the creation of several affiliated clinics and he became wellknown among celebrities including elizabeth taylor michael jackson and fashion designer donna karanbestselling authorby the early s chopra had split off from the maharishi and relocated to california where he became the executive director of the sharp institute for human potential and mindbody medicine but he eventually clashed with his bosses and in  he started the chopra center for well being by this time chopra had become an international success his first book quantum healing exploring the frontiers of mindbody medicine published in  proved to be a decent seller but it was his  release ageless body timeless mind which shot chopra into fullfledged celebrity status selling more than a million hardcover copies alone at a time when the selfhelp industry was coming into its own chopra became one of its leading faces his core message centers around the idea that the reliance on a material world complicates finding peace and happiness to chopra the answers to our health and happiness can be found internally his message has certainly resonated with the greater public in total chopra has published  books which includes  bestsellers such as the seven spiritual laws of success which have been translated into a number of different languages chopra has also contributed as a regular columnist for the san francisco chronicle and the washington postmedia projectsin june  time magazine dubbed chopra the poetprophet of alternative medicine and called him one of the top  heroes of the century  he regularly brought his message to the oprah winfrey show and was a confidante of pop superstar michael jackson his career has even seen him delve into the musicmaking business hes collaborated with a range of artists from madonna to dave stewart of the s band the eurythmics  deepak chopra is married to his longtime wife rita the chopras who have two grown children reside in californiafact checkwe strive for accuracy and fairness if you see something that doesnt look right contact uscitation informationarticle titledeepak chopra biographycomauthorbiographycom editorswebsite namethe biographycom websiteurlhttpswwwbiographycompeopledeepakchopraaccess datepublisherae television networkslast updatedapril  original published datenasharesbio newslettersign up to receive updates from bio and ae networks deepak chopra – synchrodestiny course – free download internet marketing courses gmt singaporeemail protectedritavu login cart  no products in the cart subtotal  view cart checkout facebook free download internet marketing courses tutorialsdl newnulled shop homehealth  fitness  lifestyledeepak chopra – synchrodestiny course sale deepak chopra – synchrodestiny course   price  you just pay  sale page httpwwwchopracomonlineprogramssynchrodestiny add to cart category health  fitness  lifestyle tags deepak chopra deepak chopra  synchrodestiny course synchrodestiny course description reviews  product description deepak chopra – synchrodestiny course price  you just pay  sale page httpwwwchopracomonl