 the bible the huffington post retrieved april     shermer michael march   skyhooks and cranes deepak chopra george w bush and intelligent design the huffington post retrieved november     chopra deepak august   rescuing intelligent design – but from whom the huffington post retrieved april     paul kurtz  skepticism and humanism the new paradigm transaction publishers p  isbn  retrieved april     a b coyne jerry a november   pseudoscientist rupert sheldrake is not being persecuted and is not like galileo the new republic   chopra deepak november   the perils of skepticism the huffington post retrieved april     plait phil december   deepak chopra redefining wrong discover   orzel chad october   malcolm gladwell is deepak chopra scienceblogs retrieved october     ohar george m  magic in the machine age technology and culture   – doitech   stenger victor j  quantum quackery skeptical inquirer      winners of the ig nobel prize improbable research retrieved december     the enemies of reason channel    study finds people who fall for nonsense inspirational quotes are less intelligent the huffington post december   retrieved december     pennycook gordon et al november  on the reception and detection of pseudoprofound bt judgment and decision making pennsylvania society for judgment and decision making sjdm and the european association for decision making eadm   – retrieved december     shukla aseem april   the washington post retrieved february     shukla aseem dr chopra honor thy heritage the washington post retrieved february     shukla aseem on faith panelists blog hinduism and sanatana dharma one and the same – aseem shukla the washington post retrieved july     hari m sharma b d triguna deepak chopra may   maharishi ayurveda modern insights into ancient medicine journal of the american medical association   –  pmid  doijama   financial disclosure jama    august   doijama  andrew a skolnick october   maharishi ayurveda gurus marketing scheme promises the world ete