ra is just another huckster purveying watereddown eastern wisdom mixed with pseudo science and pop psychology—to the outright damning   a b c d faceoff does god have a future nightline season  episode  transcript from the internet archive march   abc retrieved july     a b kaminer wendy  the corrosion of the american mind reviewing the age of american unreason by susan jacoby the wilson quarterly    jstor  then came scientology the science of positive thinking and more recently new age healer deepak chopras nonsensical references to quantum physics   a b scientists find a link between low intelligence and acceptance of pseudoprofound bulls the independent december   retrieved december     a b c carroll robert todd may   deepak chopra the skeptics dictionary   a b david gorski deepak chopra tries his hand at a clinical trial woo ensues retrieved  december    chamberlain adrian october   backstage a lesson in concentration from deepak chopra times colonist   chopra and chopra  pp    chopra  pp – – michael schulder may   the chopra brothers cnn   chopra sanjiv md archived december   at the wayback machine beth israel deaconess medical center retrieved may    the aiimsonians alumni site notes he joined aiims in  retrieved august    deepak chopra return of the rishi houghton mifflin harcourt  p   carl lindgren march   international dreamer – deepak chopra map magazines street editors archived from the original on july     chopra  p  deepak chopra special keynote with dr deepak chopra november  from  mins richard knox foreign doctors a us dilemma boston globe june    dr deepak k chopra us news and world report  deepak k chopra md commonwealth of massachusetts board of registration in medicine verify a physicians certification archived december   at the wayback machine american board of internal medicine  lambert craig a july  quantum healing an interview with deepak chopra md yoga journal  –   young anna m  prophets gurus and pundits rhetorical styles and public engagemen