st literature on quantum healing is almost entirely theosophical omitting the rigorous mathematics that makes quantum electrodynamics possible see doug bramwell magic of quantum physics association for skeptical enquiry retrieved december     richard dawkins interview with chopra the enemies of reason channel  uk  deepak chopra richard dawkins plays god the video updated the huffington post june    dann dulin the medicine man interview with deepak chopra au magazine   chopra   pp   –  lawrence j schneiderman  the alternative medicalization of life journal of law medicine  ethics    pmid  doijxtbx   a b c d wanjek christopher  bad medicine misconceptions and misuses revealed from distance healing to vitamin o wiley bad science series john wiley  sons pp – isbn  retrieved april     posner gary p  hardly a prayer on abcs  downtown skeptical inquirer novemberdecember   deepak deepak october   i will not be pleased – your health and the nocebo effect san francisco chronicle   dare stephen march   stephen dare interviews deepak chopra metro jacksonville   for time peter rowe truly madly deeply deepak chopra ut san diego may   p  for clinton public papers of the presidents of the united states william j clinton – january  to june   government printing office  p  for gorbachev and the quote cosmo landesman theres an easy way to save the world the sunday times may    george m ohar  magic in the machine age technology and culture    jstor  doitech   paul kurtz skepticism and humanism the new paradigm transaction publishers  p  wendy kaminer  the corrosion of the american mind the wilson quarterly    jstor    henderson mark february   junk medicine the triumph of mumbo jumbo the times book review p    francis wheen july   how mumbojumbo conquered the world a short history of modern delusions publicaffairs pp – isbn    stephen barrett a few thoughts on ayurvedic mumbojumbo retrieved april     moukheiber zina  lord of immortality forbes book review      lois malcolm  god as best